---
title: Garlic Beef Panzanella with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Zucchini
description: Panzanella is an Italian salad that combines toasty homemade croutons with veggies! Together with roasted sweet potatoes and zucchini, this salad is the perfect pairing for the easiest beef dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/garlic-beef-panzanella-adb52b44.jpg
